msgstr "Szybka konwersja formatu z natychmiastowym pobieraniem"

msgid "Which image formats are supported?"
msgstr "Jakie formaty obrazów są obsługiwane?"

msgid ""
"Input formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, BMP, and TIFF. Output formats: JPEG, "
"PNG, WebP, GIF, BMP, and TIFF. You can convert between any combination of "
"these formats."
msgstr ""
