msgstr "Dowolny obraz, nawet iPhone HEIC"

msgid "JPG, PNG, WebP, HEIC, BMP, TIFF, and GIF — including iPhone photos"
msgstr "JPG, PNG, WebP, HEIC, BMP, TIFF i GIF — w tym zdjęcia z iPhone'a"

